{"tid":1464582,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"麻煩大家冷靜d!","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:54.000Z","uid":27036,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"efa879f80acc4fb3842178cf47b22c019ee23471","tid":1464582,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"我地都係緊張香港嘅未來，可唔可以停一停止互相攻擊？<br />\n琴日成功癱瘓機場，但出現fake news散水<br />\n今日阻旅客令好多人意見不合<br />\n歸根究底係因為我地第一次搞機場不合作運動<br />\n<br />\n連續搞咗兩日好似大家都有唔同意見，會唔會考慮呢個時候暫停一下departure hall戰線？冷靜討論一個共識出黎點樣再搞機場？急，只會令我地出更多錯！希望大家停止互相攻擊！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">團結返我地自己友！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而且大家一直最擔心民意逆轉，818就係我地驗證有冇逆轉嘅時候！<br />\n<br />\n不如冷靜落黎力谷遊行，同時間再討論點樣再發動其他抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n要記住我地時刻檢討，不分化先可以打贏呢場仗！"},{"pid":"1919c675124d78c04c302d549985cd5f927475ca","tid":1464582,"uid":27036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:13:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f0d685147bdfdbcd126bfb57d621fd9a906cd4e9","tid":1464582,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05676ae5352c0b7cda7427a2cd05fbdba8936dc9","tid":1464582,"uid":84115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"小弟有一計 大家點睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/khrbckX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/khrbckX</a>"},{"pid":"bc05ab855022418cf6ccfbb3dbef6da343b14a30","tid":1464582,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f606c34ff097abd4630300eb713bcc5d599bd912","tid":1464582,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5ec78b2494e8bddb7a3df61c3c81a9d6cb406d94","tid":1464582,"uid":27036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bcdaa225f1e9d508fee7b5ef87af4be083002c3","tid":146458